---
title: Roman-Style Chicken Pasta with Tomatoes and Bell Peppers
description: This Roman-Style pasta is a heartwarming Italian stew, perfect for chilly nights. The addition of Ditalini pasta ensures no sauce gets left behind. Time to dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-au-poulet-a-la-romaine-744f0467.jpg
